28:36.506 --> 28:39.634
(SIGHS) You know a Bob Longano, Tim?

28:40.176 --> 28:42.178
He’s uh... one of your aunt’s new friends.

28:42.387 --> 28:46.599
Don’t know the name
but, like I said, he’s one of many, so...

28:46.683 --> 28:51.688
You didn’t see Bob last Saturday?
He slept over, left his coat on the couch?

28:52.021 --> 28:53.606
Didn’t see him or his coat.

28:54.399 --> 28:56.359
BALDWIN: You ever been to L.J. stereo
on Houston and third?

28:56.484 --> 28:58.027
-Nope
-No.

28:58.695 --> 29:00.905
’Cause last purchase made
on Bob Longano’s credit card

29:00.989 --> 29:03.575
before he reported it stolen
was made at that store

29:03.658 --> 29:06.536
-by a guy who fit your description.
-Wasn’t me.

29:06.619 --> 29:09.664
They’re pulling the security tape now
to prove that it was.

29:10.331 --> 29:11.916
-You back using drugs?
-No.

29:12.208 --> 29:13.501
Then why’d you steal
the credit card and cash?

29:14.753 --> 29:15.962
I didn’t take her ring.

29:16.045 --> 29:18.131
-Who do you owe money to?
-I don’t owe money.

29:18.381 --> 29:21.634
You must or you’d realize
that the only way staying out of jail

29:21.760 --> 29:24.137
-is by giving the ring back.
-You're the guy now, Tim.

29:24.304 --> 29:25.638
We’re gonna find out
where you ditched the ring.

29:25.722 --> 29:28.641
-Then you’re going to jail.
-GREG: Or get it to us right now

29:28.808 --> 29:30.310
and your aunt said
she’ll get you back in rehab.

29:30.643 --> 29:32.771
Oh, did she? That’s real sweet.

29:34.397 --> 29:35.607
Son of a bitch.

29:36.775 --> 29:39.819
-Son of a bitch.
-BALDWIN: Did you fence the ring?

29:40.612 --> 29:41.946
-Pawned it.
-BALDWIN: Where?

29:42.155 --> 29:43.531
-First and bowery.
-GREG: You didn’t think

29:43.698 --> 29:44.699
this would get back to you?

29:44.824 --> 29:46.326
I thought she’d get embarrassed

29:46.451 --> 29:48.203
that you’re looking
into her slutting around

29:48.369 --> 29:50.121
and she’d just drop it.

29:50.371 --> 29:52.373
Slutting around? That’s a little harsh

29:52.582 --> 29:54.667
for the woman who’s giving you free room
and board.

29:55.001 --> 29:57.420
You ever been around someone
who’s happy when you’re not?

29:57.712 --> 30:00.673
Somebody’s who’s been able
to completely transform their life

30:00.757 --> 30:03.593
into this insane fairy tale,
and you can’t...

30:03.676 --> 30:05.220
You can’t get away from your own past?

30:05.929 --> 30:07.889
Makes you a little bitter.

30:08.890 --> 30:10.350
Work on it in rehab.

30:12.644 --> 30:14.562
(TELEPHONE RINGING)

30:15.939 --> 30:17.899
I just don’t know what else to tell you.

30:18.274 --> 30:20.443
We found a basement dungeon in Queens

30:20.527 --> 30:22.946
where a guy was holding women
and torturing them.

30:24.322 --> 30:25.782
Really?

30:28.493 --> 30:29.702
This was found there.

30:31.996 --> 30:33.957
It got washed down the drain
In the middle of the floor,

30:34.040 --> 30:36.042
but the clasp hooked onto the grating.

30:38.294 --> 30:41.256
Inscribed with a birthday and "love, mom."

30:43.216 --> 30:44.342
I don’t know whose this is.

30:44.467 --> 30:46.803
-Is that your birthday?
-It is but...

30:47.971 --> 30:49.556
It was a gift from your mom, wasn’t it?

30:52.475 --> 30:54.978
We understand you’re not being honest
with us earlier

30:55.103 --> 30:58.022
in order to avoid having to relive
what happened in that basement.

30:58.106 --> 31:01.067
I told you nothing happened, very little.

31:01.484 --> 31:06.030
If you don’t tell us the truth now,
this guy may not go away for very long.

31:06.364 --> 31:08.241
We only have one victim who can testify.

31:08.324 --> 31:10.159
And that will get this guy
a sentence of eight years,

31:10.243 --> 31:11.911
but he’ll be out in five.

31:12.161 --> 31:14.789
If we can establish a pattern though,
he’ll never get out.

31:15.081 --> 31:17.876
Do you want what happened
to you done to somebody else?

31:18.459 --> 31:20.712
-Of course not.
-Then help us.

31:22.547 --> 31:25.049
Maybe... (SIGHS)

31:25.717 --> 31:27.927
...I was there longer than two days?

31:28.678 --> 31:31.556
-How long do you think?
-Maybe a week?

31:34.142 --> 31:35.184
Three weeks.

31:36.060 --> 31:37.437
JOHN: Were you sexually assaulted?

31:43.776 --> 31:46.029
Yes. (SOBS)

31:47.196 --> 31:48.865
-Oh, my God.
-It’s all right.

31:49.240 --> 31:51.618
No. No, it’s not. (SOBS)

31:54.162 --> 31:55.788
Did you ever see his face?

31:58.708 --> 32:00.919
He was one of the men
in the pictures you showed me.

32:01.753 --> 32:05.340
-He assaulted you?
-He humiliated me.

32:06.966 --> 32:11.262
-He raped me, put things inside me.
-ANDY: Was he alone when he did it?

32:12.013 --> 32:13.014
Sometimes there was a woman.

32:14.015 --> 32:15.892
-What does she look like?
-I don’t know.

32:16.059 --> 32:17.685
Would you recognize her
If you saw her again?

32:17.769 --> 32:20.104
GINA: I don’t know. I don’t know.

32:20.563 --> 32:22.690
But, she was definitely there,
participating?

32:23.149 --> 32:24.817
She did everything that he did.

32:26.819 --> 32:27.987
Oh, my God.

32:29.364 --> 32:30.615
Oh, my God.

32:31.908 --> 32:34.452
(SOBBING)

32:48.591 --> 32:51.636
We got another girl
who’s gonna testify against your husband.

32:51.761 --> 32:52.762
Oh, Lord.

32:52.845 --> 32:55.056
She’s also gonna testify
that you were involved.

32:55.264 --> 32:56.265
Me?

32:56.599 --> 32:58.226
What does that mean? Involved how?

32:58.351 --> 33:00.019
With the torture, the sex.

33:00.228 --> 33:02.313
No, no, no, no.
That’s just not accurate.

33:02.438 --> 33:05.316
She saw your face.
She remembers what you did to her.

33:05.400 --> 33:08.152
Well, the girl is lying
or you put ideas into her head.

33:08.236 --> 33:10.488
-Right.
-I was beaten the same as those girls.

33:10.780 --> 33:14.701
I was raped. I feared for my life.
Why am I being treated like a criminal?

33:14.826 --> 33:18.121
Testify against your husband.
It could get time off your sentence.

33:18.204 --> 33:20.373
But you playing victim ain’t gonna work.

33:23.084 --> 33:24.669
(GASPS)

33:29.382 --> 33:31.050
Paul brought home girls.

33:31.592 --> 33:32.969
They’d been drugged.

33:33.928 --> 33:35.388
He put them in the basement,

33:35.513 --> 33:37.682
then he’d go down there
and come up hours later,

33:37.849 --> 33:40.560
-sometimes covered in blood.
-Okay.

33:40.810 --> 33:43.438
When I asked him what he was doing,
he said he was a deprogrammer.

33:43.521 --> 33:44.731
No, no, no. We’re way past this.

33:44.897 --> 33:48.109
And when I said I didn’t believe him,
he beat me and threatened my life.

33:48.192 --> 33:49.819
ANDY: Get to how you participated
in the torture.

33:49.902 --> 33:51.070
Never. I never did.

33:51.279 --> 33:55.116
Do you understand? We have a girl
who saw you a girl with no reason to lie!

33:55.241 --> 33:57.785
Well, she is lying because
I was never down there!

33:58.036 --> 34:01.080
I will tell you who the girls were
that my husband kidnapped,

34:01.289 --> 34:04.000
and how long he kept them,
but I will never tell you

34:04.083 --> 34:06.294
that I had anything to do
with what happened in the basement.

34:07.336 --> 34:10.923
Now, I am sick with guilt
that I didn’t do more to help those girls,

34:11.007 --> 34:12.550
but I was scared for my life.

34:13.718 --> 34:15.219
And that’s all I’m gonna say.

34:21.100 --> 34:24.395
(GASPS) Oh, thank god.

34:24.687 --> 34:26.814
-Just as you remember it?
-Exactly.

34:27.398 --> 34:29.108
The... the kerchief’s clean, so you know.

34:29.484 --> 34:31.277
(LAUGHS) I'm sure it is.

34:31.486 --> 34:33.946
And as far as charges against your nephew,

34:34.072 --> 34:37.366
if you still have a mind
not to file and opt for rehab,

34:37.742 --> 34:39.077
there’s some recommendations I could make.

34:39.202 --> 34:40.203
I spoke to his mother,

34:40.286 --> 34:42.872
and she has a center set
for him in California.

34:42.955 --> 34:44.248
There you go. That’s for the best.

34:44.457 --> 34:45.541
I think so, too.

34:46.542 --> 34:47.543
(SIGHS) Well.

34:48.169 --> 34:50.171
I can’t thank you enough.

34:50.463 --> 34:51.464
(CHUCKLES)

34:52.048 --> 34:54.967
You’ve handled this matter
with such grace,

34:55.218 --> 34:57.512
you and detective Jones.

34:58.721 --> 35:01.599
-Uh... please tell him I said thank you.
-I will, absolutely.

35:02.934 --> 35:04.769
Well, is there anything else
you need me for?

35:04.936 --> 35:06.312
Papers to sign?

35:06.979 --> 35:08.689
Anything you’d like to talk about?

35:09.649 --> 35:12.110
Well, if something comes to mind,
you have my number.

35:15.363 --> 35:17.657
You really do have a sweetness, detective.

35:17.824 --> 35:20.827
I could tell that the first second
I saw you.

35:22.245 --> 35:23.246
Hmm.

35:29.919 --> 35:32.463
Gina Belle saw a photo array
with Susan Grady in it?

35:32.713 --> 35:33.965
But she couldn’t ID.

35:34.173 --> 35:35.800
It’s got to be worth something
that she identified

35:35.883 --> 35:37.301
there was a female present.

35:37.426 --> 35:39.053
-Could've been anyone.
-There’s only one woman

35:39.262 --> 35:41.180
-it could have been.
-VALERIE: You know it. I know it.

35:41.264 --> 35:42.265
but without a clear I.D.,

35:42.390 --> 35:44.559
and with Susan Grady playing up
the battered wife...

35:44.851 --> 35:47.228
She’ll make an immunity deal
for testimony against her husband.

35:47.770 --> 35:50.106
He’ll go away forever.
You can take comfort in that.

35:50.314 --> 35:51.941
-Yeah.
-I’ll be in touch.

35:53.651 --> 35:54.819
If the husband hadn’t lawyered up,

35:54.902 --> 35:56.154
we might have gotten him
to turn on the wife.

35:56.487 --> 35:57.655
And played them off each other,

35:57.989 --> 35:59.240
maybe found out why the hell
all this happened

35:59.323 --> 36:02.034
in the first place which now
we never will.

36:08.833 --> 36:10.459
I’m gonna get Grady to central booking.

36:12.420 --> 36:13.671
(CLEARS THROAT)

36:18.384 --> 36:20.011
(TELEPHONE RINGING)

36:20.344 --> 36:22.263
(DOOR CLOSES)

36:22.680 --> 36:23.681
I blew it bad.

36:24.432 --> 36:26.058
-Yeah.
-I’m sorry.

36:28.019 --> 36:29.312
I lost a wife, too.

36:29.896 --> 36:31.856
She was an A.D.A. She got shot in court.

36:32.481 --> 36:33.482
That’s awful.

36:33.691 --> 36:36.736
I was mad about it a long time.
I’m still mad about it.

36:37.528 --> 36:39.280
But I learned it’s got to have its place.

36:39.697 --> 36:42.241
I try to not let what happened
to Marcy get into the work,

36:42.450 --> 36:43.993
But sometimes...

36:44.118 --> 36:46.120
You want to keep yourself
emotionally involved,

36:46.662 --> 36:50.291
but when it sours the case to the victim,
Your reasons don’t matter.

36:51.584 --> 36:52.668
I know.

36:53.169 --> 36:55.630
Go easy on yourself, Hatcher.
It’ll make you a better cop.

36:56.172 --> 36:57.590
Why don’t you go home?
I’ll see you tomorrow.

37:02.345 --> 37:03.721
(DOOR OPENS)

37:04.847 --> 37:06.933
(COLONEL SQUAWKING)

37:07.058 --> 37:09.060
-Bird in there?
-He is going home.

37:09.685 --> 37:10.937
He’ll be missed.

37:11.812 --> 37:13.814
I hear the sarcasm in that, Sipowicz.

37:14.440 --> 37:16.234
And if it was you
who taught him that word,

37:16.359 --> 37:18.236
I’ll just say you won
the battle but not the war.

37:18.569 --> 37:20.238
’Cause I'll have his vocabulary
cleaned out in a week.

37:20.696 --> 37:23.366
Maybe you’re missing the point.
That bird don’t belong here.

37:23.532 --> 37:25.743
I can put in my office whatever I see fit.

37:25.952 --> 37:27.578
Plaques and tchotchkes, Yeah.

37:27.787 --> 37:30.665
But not some bird who uh...
disrupts the environment.

37:30.915 --> 37:33.834
There we go, old man Sipowicz
just don’t like to adjust.

37:34.085 --> 37:36.671
Gibson, nobody needs to be Squawked at
so loud

37:36.754 --> 37:39.048
they flinch and damn near pull their gun
or uh...

37:39.173 --> 37:41.467
reach for the phone ten times
and there’s no one there

37:41.592 --> 37:44.470
because the Colonel has learned
how to mimic the ring.

37:48.933 --> 37:51.060
I never had my own enclosed workspace,

37:51.477 --> 37:54.021
and I always had an idea
of what it would be like if I did.

37:55.064 --> 37:57.149
Maybe I went too far too fast.

37:57.733 --> 37:58.776
Maybe.

37:59.694 --> 38:00.736
I’ll work on it.

38:01.237 --> 38:02.405
(COLONEL GURGLES)

38:04.240 --> 38:07.034
Taru might be able
to put that "pretty bird"

38:07.118 --> 38:09.537
you been saying all day
onto a tape-recorded loop.

38:09.829 --> 38:11.789
That way you can just leave it
in with him overnight

38:11.872 --> 38:13.624
and get him fully cleaned out.

38:14.875 --> 38:16.294
You just now come up with that?

38:18.087 --> 38:19.130
POLICE OFFICER: Sarge.

38:23.384 --> 38:25.511
-COLONEL: Douche bag.
-I know, I know.

38:41.569 --> 38:42.653
VERONICA: Detective.

38:43.362 --> 38:44.905
I’m so glad you called.

38:45.865 --> 38:47.366
Yeah, yeah.

38:48.242 --> 38:49.660
Can I get something for you?

38:50.995 --> 38:52.496
Herbal tea, please.

38:54.707 --> 38:58.794
So, do you generally call the women
involved in your cases?

38:59.378 --> 39:01.255
-Never once.
-Why me?

39:02.423 --> 39:04.467
You, uh... (CLEARS THROAT)

39:05.134 --> 39:07.386
Pardon me. Uh, I... I don’t know
If you noticed,

39:07.511 --> 39:11.140
but I... I... I sometimes have a bit
of a... a stammer.

39:11.474 --> 39:12.933
Take your time.

39:14.352 --> 39:16.187
(SIGHS) You’re a very open person.

39:16.771 --> 39:20.733
-I try to be.
-And I... I was really just calling to ask

39:20.816 --> 39:23.569
if uh... maybe sometime
you wouldn’t mind, uh...

39:24.278 --> 39:27.490
going out and having a... a drink?

39:28.074 --> 39:31.744
You called to ask me out
in order to ask me out?

39:32.453 --> 39:34.580
What I... what I was really trying
to ask is...

39:34.705 --> 39:37.083
Detective, I’ve got, what,
15 years on you?

39:37.583 --> 39:38.584
About that.

39:38.709 --> 39:41.837
I’m gonna tell you something
I should have learned 15 years ago.

39:42.254 --> 39:44.298
-Okay.
-We’re adults.

39:44.548 --> 39:48.969
-We are.
-Consenting, vibrant, intelligent adults.

39:49.095 --> 39:51.180
-Yes.
-We can converse freely

39:51.263 --> 39:53.808
without ego or pretense.

39:54.016 --> 39:56.268
-There’s no need for games.
-I agree.

39:56.936 --> 40:00.064
Detective, do you want to have sex?

41:01.167 --> 41:03.002
You seem deep in thought.

41:03.794 --> 41:04.795
Yeah.

41:06.130 --> 41:08.507
Hmm, I sense you’re a little conflicted?

41:09.842 --> 41:13.762
-Maybe.
-Oh? You got your bell rung.

41:14.096 --> 41:16.640
That you know. You know you liked it.

41:17.349 --> 41:18.350
No doubt.

41:20.060 --> 41:22.605
Oh, but still you’re uncomfortable.

41:23.147 --> 41:25.024
-Confused.
-Hmm.

41:25.649 --> 41:26.650
Detective...

41:27.234 --> 41:31.238
I devoted many years
to complicating my life...

41:32.072 --> 41:36.243
but it’s about simplicity,
simplifying life.

41:38.954 --> 41:40.623
You’re a remarkable woman.

41:41.081 --> 41:43.626
And you’re a remarkable man.

41:44.043 --> 41:49.381
And if it wouldn’t be too much to ask,
would a young buck like yourself

41:49.632 --> 41:53.344
have another go-around in him
for an old broad like me?

41:53.677 --> 41:58.140
-I’ll do my best, ma’am.
-(CHUCKLES) Mm.

42:14.698 --> 42:19.828
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

42:42.351 --> 42:43.602
(THEME MUSIC CONCLUDES)
